{"tid":779281,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"朱凱廸: FCC 與香港人同坐一條船","createTime":"2018-08-14T09:51:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-14T09:55:27.000Z","uid":134071,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"80a8effc8b2ced02f08a5217da76da46ca1f8e73","tid":779281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:51:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><a href=\"http://thestandnews.com/politics/fcc-%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E5%9D%90%E4%B8%80%E6%A2%9D%E8%88%B9/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffcc-%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%259D%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A2%259D%25E8%2588%25B9%2F&d=Z6Mwn0o3lCmFFftg3u17jP1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=1682e28b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Ffcc-%25E8%2588%2587%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2590%258C%25E5%259D%2590%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A2%259D%25E8%2588%25B9%2F&h=5df832de\" target=\"_blank\">http://thestandnews.com/politics/fcc-%E8%88%87%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E5%90%8C%E5%9D%90%E4%B8%80%E6%A2%9D%E8%88%B9/</a></span><br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸<br />\n<br />\nFCC 與香港人同坐一條船<br />\n2018/8/14 &mdash; 10:31<br />\n<br />\n分享桑普先生這讜論：〈民族黨禁與解套之道〉。聲援民族黨和一切受牽連的人和團體，包括 FCC，是維護人權的基本態度。<br />\n<br />\n事件發展至今，有兩點值得留意。中共違諾剝奪港人普選權，刻意激起港人離心，進而以民族主義大棒加強對香港的控制。言論自由不包括講獨，經歷過去三年多次事件後，已成傳媒和大學，甚至議會的紅線。而這條紅線，正向「言論自由不包括推翻中共專政」的方向移動。在此大勢中，留港外國人群體已是剩下仍能發聲的主要群體。<br />\n<br />\n外國記者會 FCC 與香港人同坐一條船，我們以香港為家，因為相信基本人權仍受尊重；外國記者留駐香港，也是因為這裏與大陸不一樣，採訪不受限制。FCC 引火燒身，理由很簡單，如果香港連「講獨」也不行，還留下來幹什麼？梁振英以為外國記者希罕的是能否繼續以他說的「象徵式租金」租用會址，真是小人之心，貽笑大方。<br />\n<br />\n海納百川，有容乃大。香港是否仍為自由港，外國人和組織是否願意留下，是重要的證明。FCC 挺身而出捍衛核心價值，與香港人共進退。同時間，也間接向特區政府發出警號。如果 FCC 因此事遭遇任何打壓，包括取消會址租約，各國駐港總領事肯定不會袖手旁觀，事件在中美貿易戰中，可能演化為外交角力。<br />\n<br />\n當然，外國人不會為香港的存活拼命，出過聲冇用，自然會調整策略或另謀出路。一眾強國擁躉到時還會說，我們勝利啦，香港是中國人的地方，好行夾唔送。"},{"pid":"13f945af187770d89696a1b9daebe4b5176dd864","tid":779281,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"仲普選權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續選飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只剩下選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edac6403a5a836746715800c92c2ae369c3366b7","tid":779281,"uid":4493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13f945af187770d89696a1b9daebe4b5176dd864","tid":779281,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"仲普選權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續選飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只剩下選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d93de708bea3efb3d533eb633cc726855c3b8c0","tid":779281,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"13f945af187770d89696a1b9daebe4b5176dd864","tid":779281,"uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:54:15.000Z","msg":"仲普選權<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼續選飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n只剩下選舉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-14T09:55:27.000Z","msg":"陳國強都有意戰補選<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20180814/s00002/1534183869067\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180814%2Fs00002%